        <p>The training concept is an absolute breeze to do at home.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="features_box">
        <div class="feature_avatar avatar_3">
          <img src="assets/HeartFeatures.png" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="features_title">Bonding Sessions like no other</h3>
        <p>Strengthen the bond between you and your puppy.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="features_box">
        <div class="feature_avatar avatar_4">
          <img src="assets/BoneFeatures.png" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="features_title">Physical & mental workouts</h3>
        <p>Keep your dog in shape – mentally and physically..</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Care -->

    <div class="care_section">
    <h2> Connect with your Porpi </h2>
      <div class="care_container">
        <div class="care_content">
